Ability: Charisma.Requires Training: Yes.Classes: Bard.A Bard using Perform can perform the bardsong, which improves their allies' ability to fight in combat and withstand mind-affecting enemies. Perform is essential for any Bard who wants to have access to their bardsong.Check: None required. The higher the rank in this skill, the better the bardsong.Use: Select the skill to affect a 30-foot radius of allies around the singer.